{"tid":2070855,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"天意和殺機 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-06-19T11:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T09:26:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5bb3529182cd53598e5808d9d7193d5ec0e19690","tid":2070855,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:53:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200619/20939880/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200619%2F20939880%2F&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C42ydpG6lAcy7lEd76f4zig%3D&h=a2ada6c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200619%2F20939880%2F&h=75b119c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200619/20939880/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n天意和殺機 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200619/large/1592461951_a2a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200619%2Flarge%2F1592461951_a2a2.jpg&h=e1f336da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖開了幾個通宵趕工，還可以，不太累，靠意志力吧。與美術設計談封面，散會時已很晚，才開手機，充斥着「彩虹照」。<br />\n<br />\n整天都在忙，不知外頭世界。傍晚下過一場大雨後，竟出現兩條橫跨天際的雙彩虹，一條已是美景，還「兩條」，「雙」，不但罕見，且振奮人心，風雨過後，命不該絕，且添色彩。不止中環尖沙咀，全港多處包括東涌、大埔、沙田、深井、青馬大橋&hellip;&hellip;都有市民目睹奇景，還拍下來廣傳，即使不同地區角度，亦萬眾一心。<br />\n<br />\n看報導和評論：雙彩虹在東方文化中，象徵即將發生巨大的變革，也有人認為是吉兆，「變革」不一定負面，伏妖降魔重光也有彩虹作喻，天佑香港！<br />\n<br />\n雙彩虹沒殺傷力，。。。。。宇宙自然界有法則，也有天道，若天人合發生變革，亦天意，不怕，面對之。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"73bf506556d7083c1264e13a3784e43c80a2a4cd","tid":2070855,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:26:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200624/20942879/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200624%2F20942879%2F&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C42ydpG6lAcy7lEd76f4zig%3D&h=88e7963c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200624%2F20942879%2F&h=167ba2d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200624/20942879/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n日食的三年警示 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200624/large/1592895162_328f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200624%2Flarge%2F1592895162_328f.jpg&h=286993be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5月香港母親節，商場。。。。。，一片悲憤聲中，過去了。<br />\n<br />\n6月的父親節，妖。。。。。白色恐怖還有暗殺威嚇。<br />\n<br />\n由娃娃抓起的。。。。。的父親，如何過這個節？<br />\n<br />\n最詭異的，是天象。<br />\n<br />\n2020年的父親節。。。。。日食（蝕），實在太巧合。<br />\n<br />\n當月亮走到太陽與。。。。。館海旁觀賞、拍照。<br />\n<br />\n這天象之變，古人視為「天狗食日」，是人世災禍不祥之兆，人們必大聲擊鼓嚇走天狗，以求免災──嚇得走嚇不走，日月也會復原，只是苛政猛於天狗，才發生重大災難來譴責及懲罰，倘君主失德腐敗，上天動怒，意味「亡國更主，近期三月，遠期三年」。<br />\n<br />\n日食形成「上帝的金戒指」，但，會不會是邪魔的鐵鐐銬？我不信，你們信嗎？ <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"}]}